'''Lovolan''' was a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] manufacturer based in the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]]; their name was synonymous with wealth, diginity, beauty, and exclusivity as their products were both expensive and covered in ostentatious ornaments.<ref name="EGTD" />

The company was the manufacturer of the [[R-10 household droid]], a droid favored by [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]].<ref name="EGTD" />

It also manufactured [[Beauty Artist]], a droid favored by former [[Queen Mother|queen mother]] [[Ta'a Chume]].

